definitions.definition: Any of numerous freshwater decapod crustaceans in superfamily Astacoidea or Parastacoidea , resembling the related lobster but usually much smaller.

subdefinitions.definition: A freshwater crustacean (family Cambaridae ), sometimes used as an inexpensive seafood or as fish bait .
subdefinitions.label_groups: New England , Pennsylvania , Upper Midwestern US

definitions.definition: A freshwater crayfish (family Parastacidae ), such as the gilgie , marron , or yabby .
The species Thenus orientalis of the slipper lobster family ( Scyllaridae ).

main_definition: Any of numerous freshwater decapod crustaceans in superfamily Astacoidea or Parastacoidea , resembling the related lobster but usually much smaller.
secondary_definitions: ( Australia , New Zealand , South Africa ) A rock lobster (family Palinuridae ).
( Australia ) A freshwater crayfish (family Parastacidae ), such as the gilgie , marron , or yabby .
( Singapore ) The species Thenus orientalis of the slipper lobster family ( Scyllaridae ).
